title: HORIZONS | Entry One: Genborn
itunes:title: HORIZONS | Entry One: Genborn
itunes:subtitle: When a genetically-enhanced assassin is sent on a mission to hunt down terrorists on a faraway planet, she is forced to confront facts about herself that she’d rather keep buried.
description:
When a genetically-enhanced assassin is sent on a mission to hunt down terrorists on a faraway planet, she is forced to confront facts about herself that she’d rather keep buried—deep, deep down. This is Genborn, written by RK Nickel, performed by Moira Quirk and Andre Sogliuzzo.

Hosted on Acast. See acast.com/privacy for more information.
